          <p class="text-xl text-white/90 max-w-3xl leading-relaxed">{description}</p>

          <div class="bg-white/10 backdrop-blur-sm border border-white/20 p-6 md:p-8 rounded-lg">
            <p class="text-amber-300 font-black text-lg mb-3">THE 11:47PM DUI SEARCH STORY</p>
            <p class="text-white/90 leading-relaxed">Potential client arrested at 9:15pm. Released at 11:15pm. Searches "DUI lawyer near me" at 11:47pm from phone. 8 law firm websites: no case results visible, no attorney bio apparent, unclear consultation process, difficult mobile form, no bar admission visible. 1 modern site: "500+ DUI cases handled, 87% dismissal rate" prominently displayed, attorney bar admission and certification visible, "24/7 consultation request" with one-click mobile form, clear process: "Arrest → Arraignment → Motion → Dismissal." Which firm gets the 11:49pm call? For legal services, credibility visible = you win cases = hire you. Process clear = professional = trust = retainer signed.</p>
