        <p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed">Month 1 results: 32 consultations (up from 8, 300% increase), 19 retained cases at $6,000 average = $114,000 revenue (up from $24,000, 375% increase). Google ranking: page 1 position 3 for "Phoenix DUI lawyer." Case results page most visited. Blog articles driving organic traffic: "What to Do After DUI Arrest in Arizona" (1,200 monthly visitors). Month 3: 41 consultations, 24 retained cases = $144,000 revenue. Net profit increase: $108,000/month on $42/month investment. ROI: 257,000% in 90 days. Attorney quote: "The case results page prints money. Clients see '87% dismissal rate' and hire us instantly."</p>
      </div>

      <!-- BREAKDOWN -->
      <div class="bg-gray-50 border-[3px] border-gray-200 p-6 md:p-8">
        <h3 class="text-xl font-black text-gray-900 mb-6">THE 90-DAY BREAKDOWN</h3>
        <div class="grid md:grid-cols-4 gap-4">
          <div class="bg-white p-4 rounded-lg border border-gray-200">
            <p class="text-3xl font-black text-amber-600">300%</p>
            <p class="text-sm text-gray-600">Month 1 Consultation Increase</p>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-white p-4 rounded-lg border border-gray-200">
            <p class="text-3xl font-black text-amber-600">$120K</p>
            <p class="text-sm text-gray-600">Additional Revenue Year 1</p>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-white p-4 rounded-lg border border-gray-200">
            <p class="text-3xl font-black text-amber-600">Page 1</p>
